edu.uidaho.junicon.interpreter.transformer

Class Transform

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.uidaho.junicon.interpreter.transformer.Transform
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITransform

    public class Transform
extends Object
implements ITransform
    The Transform class supports building and applying transform chains. Transform chains will return the original node if there are no transforms to apply, i.e., have idempotent behavior. The transform() and deconstruct() methods are thread-safe. The transform building, transformDocument(), and transformNode() methods are not thread-safe. The base URL to resolve relative imports and includes is set from the filename, or may be explicitly set by setBaseUrl() prior to adding a transform.
